Because if they did then the NTSB wouldn’t be calling for members of the public to send in any photo or video evidence so they can determine the events causing the crash surely that’s not concluding thorough findings and thorough facts!!! Why did this pilot take the risk??? When he clearly had poor visibility ??? It seems he had ZERO visibility judging by the outcome!!! why the hell was this flight permitted to go ahead in the first place when the weather conditions were as bad as it was??  This tragedy could have been avoided it should never have happened in the first place !!
